43
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da.

44
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je to samo nekako snimalo.

45
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam poput, dobro, učinio sam to u siječnju.

46
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,959
[SPEAKER_00] Mislio sam da će se to dogoditi u novoj godini.

47
